---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Testimonials | Nick Sammons Realtor">
	<main class="relative z-0">
		<section class="py-16 md:py-32 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
			<span class="text-xs font-bold text-gold-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Success Stories</span>
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-8xl font-serif tracking-tight leading-none">Exceptional <span class="italic text-stone-500">Exchanges.</span></h1>
		</section>

		<section class="py-12 md:py-20 px-6 lg:px-12">
			<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16">
				<!-- Review 1: Zachary -->
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "Nick Sammons was great for helping us find our dream home. He was very knowledgeable through the whole process, and was very good at communicating at every step of the way. I'll never use another realtor!"
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Zachary</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Review 2: Ryan -->
                <div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "Nick Sammons was absolutely incredible to work with! He showed us a gorgeous home in North Georgia and really took the time to answer every single question we had about the property and the area. From the start, Nick’s professionalism and expertise were evident."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Ryan</p>
                </div>

				<!-- Review 3: Colin -->
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "My Fiancée & I told Nick what kind of home we wanted & a couple of different areas we wanted to look around. Nick was quick to research and send us homes that were relevant to us. No wasted time sending us homes that didn't fit our vision."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Colin</p>
                </div>

				<!-- Review 4: Lindsey -->
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "Nick helped my husband, my in-laws and I find the perfect piece of land! He was so patient, hard-working, and very knowledgeable when it came to our questions and meeting our needs!!!!!! Nick worked diligently from helping us find land to the closing process."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Lindsey</p>
                </div>

				<!-- Review 5: Cole -->
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "Nick thank you so much for your help. Your care and attention to detail was exactly what my wife and I were looking for in this stressful process. You took the stress out of our hands and answered any questions we had. I would recommend this young smart man to anyone looking for real estate help!"
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Cole</p>
                </div>

				<!-- Review 6: Dray B -->
				<div class="space-y-4 md:space-y-6 p-6 md:p-10 bg-white shadow-xl border-l-4 border-gold-400">
                    <div class="flex gap-1 text-gold-500">
                        <span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span><span>★</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-stone-600 italic font-serif text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
                        "We are very picky in our household. Nobody wants to commit to a home that they don’t love. Nick understood that.. over the course of 6 months, he personally toured 47 houses with us and took us to Arby’s after to discuss our opinions every time."
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-navy-900">— Dray B</p>
                </div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>